[~steveyeom2017], is this a duplicate of HIVE-18610? Or does it still exist in master?

Cc [~gopalv]
Cautiously speaking, it seems to exist in master from my testing.
[~steveyeom2017]: are you mixing up internal and external tickets? The EAR references makes no sense for Apache JIRAs - I removed the one in the descriptions.
I have reproduced the test case failure in the current master, cautiously speaking, in my environment.
This is broken because the constant structs are  being constructed with Struct(Int, Int) and they don't compare with Struct(Long,Long) from the bigint on the Table side.
Cc [~ashutoshc]

A better patch might be to change constant side if it is smaller in type than the
column side since the conversion helper takes larger type as common type 
at least for the test case.
patch 01 is not p-tested. So the same patch is added as patch 02.
